and I wanna obey all of it

00:37:23.919 --> 00:37:25.759
because I want your blessing.

00:37:25.759 --> 00:37:26.839
I want your blessing.

00:37:26.839 --> 00:37:27.679
Let's pray.

00:37:27.679 --> 00:37:28.519
Father, we love you.

00:37:29.319 --> 00:37:30.159
Thank you for loving us.

00:37:30.159 --> 00:37:30.999
Thank you for your word.

00:37:30.999 --> 00:37:32.799
I thank you for the truth contained therein.

00:37:32.799 --> 00:37:35.559
And as we can look at examples from the Old Testament,

00:37:35.559 --> 00:37:37.639
we find that Paul said this

00:37:37.639 --> 00:37:39.239
as he's writing to the church in Corinth,

00:37:39.239 --> 00:37:44.239
that they were written as in samples to us

00:37:44.239 --> 00:37:48.519
for our learning, for our admonition.

00:37:48.519 --> 00:37:50.599
And Lord, I pray that we would take heed

00:37:50.599 --> 00:37:53.159
to what we read in the Old Testament account

00:37:53.159 --> 00:37:55.479
of the children of Israel and their behavior,

00:37:55.479 --> 00:37:58.359
and that we would analyze and evaluate our own lives

00:37:59.199 --> 00:38:01.559
and determine, are we walking in your way or no?

00:38:02.879 --> 00:38:06.199
Lord, we know deep down,

00:38:06.199 --> 00:38:10.839
we know your Holy Spirit convicts us.

00:38:10.839 --> 00:38:14.279
You're so gracious to deal with us as individuals.

00:38:14.279 --> 00:38:16.639
You're so long-suffering.

00:38:16.639 --> 00:38:20.719
And I pray, God, that we would be responsive to you,

00:38:20.719 --> 00:38:21.919
that we would just determine

00:38:21.919 --> 00:38:25.639
that we're gonna live according to your word.

00:38:25.639 --> 00:38:26.719
Bless our time of prayer.

00:38:26.719 --> 00:38:28.039
We pray that through all that's said and done,

00:38:28.719 --> 00:38:30.959
that we'd be glorified for it's in Christ's name we pray.

00:38:30.959 --> 00:38:31.799
Amen.

